545
00:21:44.240 --> 00:21:47.870
Four thousand warriors? It's very impressive, recruiting so many.

546
00:21:47.870 --> 00:21:51.790
But none will make it to the port!

547
00:21:52.710 --> 00:21:56.590
I won't give them even
the slimmest chance at taking revenge!

548
00:21:58.760 --> 00:22:01.590
Go to hell, Red Scabbard specters!

549
00:22:01.930 --> 00:22:07.260
Wallow in the despair of
isolation and impotence!

550
00:22:11.600 --> 00:22:14.310
Present Day


Tokage Port

Udon

551
00:22:15.020 --> 00:22:16.820
Stop, all of you!

552
00:22:16.820 --> 00:22:19.780
Taking that small boat is suicide!

553
00:22:21.530 --> 00:22:25.820
Let us regroup and begin anew
when we get another chance!

554
00:22:25.820 --> 00:22:28.120
If we miss this opportunity...

555
00:22:29.080 --> 00:22:31.540
we will have to wait a whole year.

556
00:22:32.870 --> 00:22:39.420
But... we cannot hide any longer.
They will soon learn how we liberated Udon.

557
00:22:40.340 --> 00:22:45.180
Kaido's entire army
will descend to hunt the rebels,

558
00:22:47.220 --> 00:22:51.220
and we can no longer continue
to steal their food.

559
00:22:51.220 --> 00:22:55.400
Before we departed Kuri,
you surely heard what happened.

560
00:22:56.730 --> 00:23:01.610
The people of Okobore Town,
who believed in our great struggle...

561
00:23:01.610 --> 00:23:03.280
were burned alive.

562
00:23:04.150 --> 00:23:05.530
Among them...

563
00:23:06.490 --> 00:23:08.070
was my wife.

564
00:23:11.330 --> 00:23:13.040
Please allow us to go!

565
00:23:16.000 --> 00:23:17.170
No...!

566
00:23:17.170 --> 00:23:22.670
Do you want us to flee and live in disgrace?!

567
00:23:23.760 --> 00:23:26.260
And what of me...?

568
00:23:26.260 --> 00:23:30.390
We want you to live on with Princess Hiyori!

569
00:23:30.390 --> 00:23:32.640
Do not be so selfish!

570
00:23:34.350 --> 00:23:37.810
Even your father had no support at first!

571
00:23:37.810 --> 00:23:41.820
If we had not met Lord Oden...

572
00:23:41.820 --> 00:23:46.740
...we would not have become samurai,
immature as we were.

573
00:23:47.160 --> 00:23:49.870
That is why we want to be...

574
00:23:50.530 --> 00:23:55.500
Lord Oden's samurai retainers...
until the very end.

575
00:23:56.920 --> 00:23:58.330
Do not go!

576
00:23:58.670 --> 00:24:00.500
Do not go, Kin'emon!

577
00:24:00.500 --> 00:24:02.750
Do not go!

578
00:24:02.750 --> 00:24:06.170
I cannot bear to lose even one more person!

579
00:24:09.010 --> 00:24:11.010
Listen, men!

580
00:24:11.550 --> 00:24:18.520
This centuries-old policy of national isolation
is deeply tied to the Kozuki Clan.

581
00:24:19.270 --> 00:24:20.480
However...

582
00:24:21.230 --> 00:24:23.320
the time will eventually come!

583
00:24:24.070 --> 00:24:27.570
Before the tides begin to turn worldwide,

584
00:24:27.570 --> 00:24:30.410
we must open the borders of Wano!

585
00:24:53.430 --> 00:24:58.520
Forty-one years ago, in the Flower Capital...

586
00:24:59.980 --> 00:25:02.810
Kozuki Oden has returned!

587
00:25:03.230 --> 00:25:04.440
Hide your wives!

588
00:25:04.440 --> 00:25:06.190
Your daughters, too...!

589
00:25:06.650 --> 00:25:08.320
Even the livestock!

590
00:25:11.660 --> 00:25:14.410
He failed to set sail again!

591
00:25:14.410 --> 00:25:16.580
He wants to get out of here that badly?!

592
00:25:17.870 --> 00:25:22.880
There was a very popular man in the capital.

593
00:25:34.680 --> 00:25:37.640
It is so restrictive!
